@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_llgyiq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (v1 - (wp.exp(v2 + 0.14) - (v1 + 0.05 + v1 + 0.12)))
    v1 = (0.34 * wp.cos(v1))
    tmp = 0.02
    v0 = ((wp.exp(v1 + 0.82) * 0.34) + wp.abs((tmp + 0.88 / v0 + 0.17)))
    data[tid] = v0
